a:260:{i:0;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2390997668128053997";}i:1;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEuh7YLj1rt";}i:2;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599249155;}i:3;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:1338:"This has seemed like the busiest week of my life! Anyone else? It's just something, or multiple things, every single day, plus school, and I'm not even back to work at the preschool yet 🥴

I woke up this morning absolutely exhausted and knew I needed to show my body some love. I decided on 30 minutes of restorative yoga, and it totally got the spot. 

I could stop "running" and gave my body and mind permission to just be present for a half an hour. No where but my yoga mat.

Check out my stories to see ALL the oils that I used before my practice, but aromatouch was one of them. This is one of my favorite oils for yoga because it's amazing for tense or tight muscles. 

When people tell me that they can't practice yoga because they aren't flexible enough, I usually say, "honey, me too." My hamstrings and lower back are always tight and tense!

It's a little frustrating when I can't fold as deep as I would like to, but that always comes with time. Respect yourself enough to be okay with that.

For my hamstrings, I makes sure to always bend my knees in any forward folding motion, so that it specifically targets those hammy muscles. For my lower back, I make sure that I'm focusing on lifting and lengthening up instead of how deep I can fold. And of course for both, I apply aromatouch before hand to relax those muscles.";}i:4;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:5;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:0;}i:6;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEuh7YLj1rt";}i:7;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:248:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/118709469_939641549868906_2137089756808990201_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_ohc=iHwfxgYRejMAX8y0_ZM&_nc_tp=18&oh=3de618b2f247ffc661258d4cb98c2eda&oe=5F7CDC06";}i:8;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:9;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:39167454242;}i:10;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:11;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:12;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:13;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2390997459899324690";}i:14;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEuh4WQKRkS";}i:15;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599249130;}i:16;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:331:"🍀🍃🌿🌱

