#ALOVESPLITS 
September 1-10, 2020 

Dying to do the splits!! 

Achieving the splits stretch means impressive flexibility in your hips, glutes and hamstrings! 
We will explore different kinds of postures that will help you to develop your flexibility and range of motion over time to ultimately achieve your split goal! 
Together with us , we want you to feel the love of splits!! 

