🥳 NEW CHALLENGE 🥳

#ALOtOfBasics September 01 - 10

With all the inspirational Yoga practices on social medias & our constant quest for more advanced asanas, sometimes we lose ourselves in the practice. September is National Yoga Month & hence, a perfect time to reconnect with the foundational poses of Yoga & remember how & why we began our yoga journey in 😊 No matter what level of an Yogi you are, join us for 10 days, as we go back to the basics & spotlight the poses that our practice is grounded on! We will share tips & insight on what each pose means for us & share information on how each pose provides the foundation for more advanced postures.
.
Posture list:
⛰Day 1: Tadasana/Samasthitihi
🤗Day 2: Uttanasana
💪🏽Day 3: Virabhadrasana 1
📏Day 4: Kumbhakasana
🧍‍♀️Day 5: Balasana
Day 6: Adho Mukha Svanasana
Day 7: Virabhadrasana 2
Day 8: Vrikshasana
Day 9: Bhujangasana
Day 10: Padmasana/ Savasana
.
